Automated Chicken Coop Door Controller

The coopdoor.py script uses Astral and Scheduler to automate the opening and closing of the chicken coop door.

The following python modules will need to be installed on the Raspberry Pi:

gpiozero
schedule
astral

Please refer to the Wiki page for details on setting the hardware up.

GPIO pins used:

GPIO Pins used in this project

coopdoor.py
14 - Door Motor Open - Solid Brown
15 - Door Motor Close - White/Brown
18 - Open Button - Solid Green
23 - Close Button - White/Green


control.py - Not yet published on github.com
5 - Coop light relay
17 - Coop light on/off button. - Solid Blue
22 - LCD display on/off.
